---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
import PageHeader from "@/components/PageHeader.astro"
---

<Layout title="Strategic Plan 2025-2030 | KidsCommons">
  <PageHeader
    title="Strategic Plan 2025–2030"
    description="Our five-year roadmap to enhance the visitor experience, grow our educational impact, and strengthen our community."
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: "About", href: "/about" },
      { label: "Strategic Plan", href: "/about/strategic-plan" },
    ]}
    color="purple"
  />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-gradient-to-br from-kc-purple/5 to-kc-blue/5 p-8 sm:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Executive Summary</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
          Today's youth and their families face a variety of intertwined challenges that impact the
          quality and accessibility of their future opportunities. These include a rising mental health
          crisis and economic disparities, compounded by the aftermath of the pandemic limiting
          educational prospects for children. Despite these obstacles, they offer an opportunity for
          KidsCommons to enhance our collective resilience and vitality, advocating for systemic change.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
          Our plan focuses on empowering children and families to become confident, lifelong learners
          and catalysts for change. Through collaborative efforts with community partners, we have
          witnessed remarkable instances of creativity, resilience, and resourcefulness, shaping a
          brighter future for children.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Methodology</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Phase 1: Assessment</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              Gathering data from KidsCommons surveys and meetings with a variety of internal and
              external stakeholders.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Phase 2: Vision</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              KidsCommons staff had several round table discussions to review past strategic plans to
              decide what was still relevant and what had changed over the last 5 years. That, along
              with community surveys and ACM data, created a picture of our future organization.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Phase 3: Implementation</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              KidsCommons staff will further develop these objectives by identifying actionable tasks
              to achieve day-to-day elements of each priority.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Our Mission & Vision</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-kc-purple">Mission</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              KidsCommons is a fun, safe, and inviting place that nurtures exploration, collaboration,
              and creativity within all children and their caregivers. It is a place to learn about our
              community and our world.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-kc-blue">Vision</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              KidsCommons endeavors to be a vibrant learning hub that enriches the life of every child
              through engaging and collaborative play with their caregivers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Strategic Priorities</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
          Our strategic plan for the next five years focuses on five key priorities. We are excited to
          embark on this journey and look forward to continuing to serve children and families with
          engaging and educational experiences.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-kc-red/10 text-sm font-bold text-kc-red">1</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Enhancing the Visitor Experience</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Revamp and update existing exhibits to ensure they are engaging, educational, and aligned with current learning standards.</li>
              <li>Introduce new interactive exhibits that cater to different age groups and learning styles.</li>
              <li>Implement a visitor feedback system to gather input from families and children.</li>
              <li>Provide opportunities to families in need with free or reduced admission, camp scholarships, and discounted event tickets.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-kc-blue/10 text-sm font-bold text-kc-blue">2</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Growing Our Educational Impact</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Develop and implement new educational programs integrating STEAM concepts and hands-on learning experiences.</li>
              <li>Collaborate with local schools and educators to offer field trips, workshops, and curriculum-aligned programs.</li>
              <li>Create partnerships with community organizations to provide outreach programs and resources for underserved children and families.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-kc-green/10 text-sm font-bold text-kc-green">3</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Building Sustainability & Growth</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Develop new revenue streams, such as corporate partnerships, sponsorships, and fundraising events.</li>
              <li>Increase our membership base and develop new membership benefits to attract and retain members.</li>
              <li>Invest in infrastructure upgrades to ensure our facilities are well-maintained and up-to-date.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-kc-purple/10 text-sm font-bold text-kc-purple">4</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Increase Community Engagement & Communication</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Host community events, family nights, and outreach programs to engage families from diverse backgrounds.</li>
              <li>Partner with local businesses and organizations to sponsor events, exhibits, and programs.</li>
              <li>Collaborate with local artists and performers to bring creative and cultural experiences to the museum.</li>
              <li>Develop a comprehensive marketing and communications strategy to promote the museum's programs to a broader audience.</li>
              <li>Utilize social media platforms, email marketing, and community partnerships to engage with families.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-kc-red/10 text-sm font-bold text-kc-red">5</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold">Strengthen Organizational Capacity</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Develop a strategic fundraising plan to increase revenue and secure long-term sustainability.</li>
              <li>Recruit and retain a diverse, skilled staff team passionate about early childhood education and play-based learning.</li>
              <li>Provide ongoing professional development opportunities for staff to enhance their skills and knowledge.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Overarching Lens</h2>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-card p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            Our efforts within each Strategic Priority will be assessed through the overarching
            perspectives of Diversity, Equity, Access, and Inclusion (DEAI). Each objective, along with
            its corresponding implementation and evaluation strategies, will undergo scrutiny through
            these lenses. The museum recognizes the essential nature of DEAI at the core of all its
            initiatives and is committed to integrating these principles into our operations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
